data.description: This 3 bedroom two bath home has a lot to offer including, two storage sheds for all your crafts and gardening supplies. The large front deck is perfect for relaxing or entertaining and plenty of parking with a nice carport. Enter the good sized living room off the front deck. The kitchen has plenty of storage with a pantry. All of the appliances are in great condition including washer and dryer. The master suite features a big walk in closet and master bath with separate tub and shower. The other two bedrooms are on the opposite side of the home with a full bath. Close to Branson Landing and the 76 strip!! Come see it today!!
